                                    <div class="compile-note">
                                        <em>{"Note: The PL/SW compiler currently implements the lexer stage. \
                                              Full compilation (parser \u{2192} codegen \u{2192} assembly output) \
                                              is under development in the sw-cor24-plsw project."}</em>
